fields.name: Men's Tennis
fields.description: Expect the men's tennis team to be one of the nation's most improved NCAA Division I teams in 2014. The team played the 2013 season with an almost entirely rebuilt roster coming off an NCAA Sweet 16 campaign in 2012. In 2014, Carolina returns five of six starters from last year's singles lineup and has added one of the best recruiting classes in school history.
